{"type":null,"faqId":12497,"title":"D2-0082  彩信是否受文件大小/视频格式/分辨率等因素限制?","answer":"<p style=\"margin-left:63.8pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">1.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">视频和音频文件超过规定大小（通常是</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">300k</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）则无法添加为附件。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:63.8pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">2.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">图片文件过大时会自动压缩图片分辨率，再以附件添加到彩信中，接收方收到的图片文件也是低分辨率的图片。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:63.8pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">3.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">视频文件一般支持</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">3gp</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">AVI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">格式。在短信中录制视频时，会模糊视频以增加视频时间长度。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3356","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1399446897000,"seriesProductName":"D2-0082","visitedTimes":10,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"k